{"tid":2128050,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"盛傳任黃之鋒Plan B 梁凱晴今報名戰九東","createTime":"2020-07-27T16:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T05:32:30.000Z","uid":123587,"like":27,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3b7b48a18d08d6b4929361682766c4149aa6ec","tid":2128050,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:29:03.000Z","msg":"新一屆立法會選舉提名期本周五截止，選舉主任今日（27日）共接獲20份提名表格，至今共接獲101份提名表格。其中被視為黃之鋒Plan B的觀塘區議員梁凱晴，今天報名循九東參選。<br />\n<br />\n新西方面，何君堯領四人KOL出選爭冧莊；九西則有報稱獨立、獲田北俊希望聯盟支持的潘焯鴻報名。"},{"pid":"7771b6200f46a1bff9bb9516a720268feabc6b62","tid":2128050,"uid":123587,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"G持凱晴BB"},{"pid":"e5be9baa9e051e391cddf89a058ddd713948fdf9","tid":2128050,"uid":112551,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:29:33.000Z","msg":"大波妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1685cafb9b58cc5e7184ab654da41189509963a2","tid":2128050,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caa3333e4374130989eb388cbd6bc2306673285","tid":2128050,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e5be9baa9e051e391cddf89a058ddd713948fdf9","tid":2128050,"uid":112551,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:29:33.000Z","msg":"大波妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"咪色拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"